---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — Nolte" description="How Nolte collects, uses, and protects your information.">

  <header class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
    <h1>Privacy <em>Policy</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-subtext">Last updated: March 27, 2026</p>
  </header>

  <div class="prose legal-prose">

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly — your name, email address, and company name when you submit a form on our site. We do not collect sensitive financial or identity information through our website.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Respond to your inquiry within one business day</li>
      <li>Create a record in our CRM to manage our conversation</li>
      <li>Personalize our communication based on your needs</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not use your information for automated marketing sequences, retargeting ads, or resale to third parties.</p>

    <h2>Analytics</h2>
    <p>We use PostHog for product analytics to understand how visitors use our site. PostHog collects anonymized usage data including page views, scroll depth, and session duration. We do not use this data to identify individual visitors. Bot traffic and automated crawlers are excluded from analytics collection.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use minimal cookies for analytics purposes only. We do not use cookies for advertising, retargeting, or cross-site tracking. You can disable cookies through your browser settings without affecting your experience on our site.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Your form submissions are processed through:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Netlify</strong> — form handling and hosting</li>
      <li><strong>Clarify</strong> — CRM for managing client relationships</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personally identifiable information to outside parties. We do not use Google AdSense, Facebook Pixel, or third-party advertising services.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>All data transmitted through our site is encrypted via SSL/TLS. We do not store payment information or sensitive credentials on our servers.</p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may request access to, correction of, or deletion of your personal information at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:contact@nolte.io">contact@nolte.io</a>.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our services are not directed to individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.</p>

    <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy? Contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@nolte.io">contact@nolte.io</a>.</p>
    <p>Nolte (Moxie Media Group Inc)<br>2021 Guadalupe St #260<br>Austin, TX 78705</p>

  </div>

</Base>

<style>
  .legal-prose {
    max-width: 640px;
  }
  .legal-prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }
</style>
